      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s pristine inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and drives like a dream, this is the one. Come check it out, you\u2019re going to love it!",
