    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This A80-generation Supra Turbo represents a pinnacle of factory-spec preservation. At its heart is the 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six, featuring a sequential forced induction system that maintains peak volumetric efficiency across the power band. The drivetrain is anchored by the Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox, feeding power to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis exhibits zero structural fatigue, with all factory-spec double-wishbone suspension components and bushings showing no signs of degradation. The engine bay is immaculate, with no evidence of thermal stress on the wiring loom or fluid seepage from the valve covers. This is an investment-grade specimen with a pristine service history and original aerodynamic bodywork.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
