    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in showroom-equivalent condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover. Inside, the cabin retains that fresh new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment to the heated seating\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at the original dealership with a complete, chronological file of maintenance records included. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line: tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has never seen a winter road or a rainy day.",
      "price": 44500.0,
