      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is a total stunner! This car is in truly incredible condition; honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, and it drives just as perfectly as it looks. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine shape, this is definitely the one for you. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
