      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of the S54B32 high-revving platform. This specimen features a meticulously maintained individual throttle body (ITB) setup and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system for optimal cam phasing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual, feeding power to a variable M-differential lock with zero lash. Crucially, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates, addressing the chassis's primary structural vulnerability. Suspension geometry is factory-perfect, utilizing refreshed bushings and Sachs dampers. Every fluid analysis confirms the mechanical integrity of this concours-level vehicle.",
